docs.lead_paragraph: A YOUNG mother was wheeling a baby in a gocart at Eighth Avenue and Forty-third Street when the child dropped its rubber teething ring. It rolled through a fleck of saliva, not entirely dry, to the curb, where a polite small boy caught it.

headline.main: New System of Physical Training in Schools; Not Merely Gymnastics and Athletics, But Medical Inspection and the Teaching of Health Habits Involved in Dr. Finley's Plan
